visualizer.data
Class DataLoader

java.lang.Object
  visualizer.data.DataLoader

public class DataLoader
extends java.lang.Object

DataLoader contains two methods to load data from a DataSet into a GlyphTable. The first one, loadTable, gets the data from a DataTable, the second one, loadCube, receives the data from a DataCube.

Author:
Rene Wegener
